<plot>Jessica and Steve are on the road headed for a new life. Late night on their rainy drive Steve starts to doze at the wheel and almost crashes into a truck. Deciding he better pull over for both their safety, they set camp in the remote hills of West Virginia. A little nervous about her surroundings, Jessica forces herself to fall asleep in their little pup tent. A few hours later she is awakened by the dripping sound of the tent leaking and what happens next promises to change her life forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?160173</url></doc>
